collections.name: Echoes of Empire, The Wall Street Legacy Series
collections.description: Step into a moment suspended in time — a golden age of ambition, revolution, and power. The Wall Street Legacy Series is more than art. It’s a gateway. Each piece in this exclusive collection resurrects the heartbeat of 1913 — the moment the modern financial world was born. Streets carved in stone. Crowds marching into history. Towers scraping the heavens before skyscrapers even had a name. Horses and men, ambition and shadow — captured in the raw, honest strokes of my grandfather’s pencil. This piece was originally published in a Swiss newspaper in 1913, and drawn entirely by hand in December 1925, in the very same city where Ethereum would be born — Zug, Switzerland, one century later. From the cradle of capitalism to the birthplace of Web3: a full circle, encoded in gold. Today, Zug is globally known as Crypto Valley — the epicenter of blockchain innovation. Digitally revived over 100 years later, this series fuses ancestral memory with modern brilliance. Certificate sent post-sale.

collections.name: Changes
collections.description:
Changes is primarily a construct consisting of four angled panels. When
rotated by 90° each, the optical illusions shown create four chess
fields, each with its own functionality. The playful ease with which the
construct comes across gives no indication of the difficulties that had
to be overcome in creating the changes.
In part two of the changes, the chess pieces appear and the construct is
brought to a new level. The optical illusions no longer play a role in
this clip. The white pawn appears to float down from heaven. It is not
without reason that the black pawn rotates from diagonally below to the
chess field and then breaks through it to reach its position.
In the third part, a small game excerpt begins in which the white pawn
is defeated and has to leave the stage of the chessboard downwards. It
is essentially beaten by the black pawn, which then immediately takes
its new place on the playing field. Changes continues...

collections.name: Ethereal Biomes
collections.description:
🌿 Ethereal Biomes

Where nature remembers and machines begin to dream.

Ethereal Biomes is a curated NFT art collection exploring the delicate convergence of organic life and intelligent design. Set in a post-organic world where forests shimmer with data and rivers flow with memory, each 1/1 artwork reveals a tranquil yet otherworldly biome—part nature, part machine, fully alive.

Rendered in a detailed, semi-realistic style with a touch of magical realism, the collection captures moments of quiet beauty in landscapes shaped by both evolution and invention.

Each piece is accompanied by immersive lore, atmospheric variants, and collector-exclusive content that expands the world behind the image.

⸻

🔹 What You’ll Discover:
	•	Biomechanical creatures and sentient landscapes
	•	Holographic flora, glowing rivers, and glitch-born anomalies
	•	A growing narrative told through visuals, words, and sound
	•	Unlockable content: high-resolution artworks, alternate versions, and bespoke lore

Each NFT is a unique digital collectible derived from original artwork featured in the coloring book. These aren’t just adorable Easter Frenchies — they’re the first-ever NFTs born from the pages of this playful and imaginative series.

collections.name: Crypto Flatworld AI
collections.description:
Flatworld NFT is a unique collection of 2D characters, inspired by the famous Flatland (Flatworld). In this geometric setting, each NFT represents a unique life form controlled by its own AI agent. These are not ordinary NFTs - they are driven by AI agents and exhibit changing colors, outlines, and intelligence.
In Crypto Flatworld, each NFT is not just artwork, it is a living entity with a complete life, controlled by its own AI agent. These agents navigate, make decisions, adapt, and integrate into the future of this vibrant virtual environment.
Your NFT will become a wise scholar, brave warrior, or even a mysterious thinker. Evolve and strengthen to become a core contributor to Flatworld. Join this exploration and become a central part of a digitally governed metaverse - true, harmonious, and filled with intelligent AI exchanges.
